From: =?UTF-8?q?=C3=98yvind=20Harboe?= <oyvind.harboe@zylin.com>
Date: Mon, 7 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 35/35] fix: remove mock-openroad bazel_dep after inlining

mock-openroad was inlined into bazel-orfs as a regular package.
It no longer exists as a separate Bazel module, so the bazel_dep
must be removed.

Signed-off-by: =?UTF-8?q?=C3=98yvind=20Harboe?= <oyvind.harboe@zylin.com>
---
 MODULE.bazel | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/MODULE.bazel b/MODULE.bazel
--- a/MODULE.bazel
+++ b/MODULE.bazel
@@ -8,7 +8,6 @@

 bazel_dep(name = "bazel-orfs")
-bazel_dep(name = "mock-openroad", version = "0.0.1")
 bazel_dep(name = "rules_python", version = "1.2.0")
 bazel_dep(name = "rules_shell", version = "0.6.1")

